### **2. 26_APICheckPulse**  
**Description:**  
Batch-checks endpoints and displays real-time API health and latency diagnostics.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# APICheckPulse - Real-Time API Status Monitor

APICheckPulse monitors availability, speed, and error behavior of APIs and microservices.

## Features
- Parallelized HTTP checks  
- Burst and delay alerts  
- Export to JSON or CSV  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/26_APICheckPulse.git
cd 26_APICheckPulse
python monitor.py
